!!!
%html
  %head
    %meta{:content => "text/html; charset=UTF-8", "http-equiv" => "Content-Type"}/
  %body
    %h1
      Order Placed - #{@order.id}
    %p
      Your order has been placed! Products ordered:
    %p
      %table
      - @order.order_products.each do |op|
        %tr
          %td= op.product.name
          %td= op.quantity